txt.en: You have defeated many dwarf-wights in Bâr Maenath.
Terrible dwarf-wights stalk the old treasury of Bâr Maenath.
You have defeated many dwarf-wights in Bâr Maenath and put the remains of those unfortunate Stout-axes to rest.
Although it pained you to see your kindred in such a state, you have done well to put them to rest and break the enchantments put upon them by the evils of Minas Morgul.
Bâr Maenath can be found in the western reaches of the Circle of Death.\n\nYou have encountered dwarf-wights in Bâr Maenath and should defeat them.

You have encountered terrible dwarf-wights within Bâr Maenath.

These dwarf-wights appear to be of Stout-axe origin, but whatever life they once possessed is now gone.

You should defeat the dwarf-wights in Bâr Maenath.
